Package gate.plugin.learningframework.data

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    InstanceRepresentation
    Common interface to our own representations of learning instances.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Attribute
    Class that describes a single attribute/feature.
    Attributes
    Describes all Attributes/features of a dataset.
    CorpusRepresentation
    The base class of all classes that handle the representation of instances.
    CorpusRepresentationLibSVM  
    CorpusRepresentationMallet
    Common base class for Mallet for classification and Mallet for sequence tagging.
    CorpusRepresentationMalletRelated
    The base class of all classes that are somehow related or dependent on the Mallet instance list and Mallet pipes.
    CorpusRepresentationMalletSeq  
    CorpusRepresentationMalletTarget
    This represents a corpus in Mallet format where we have a single feature vector and single target.
    CorpusRepresentationVolatileBase
    Common base class for non Mallet volatile representations.
    CorpusRepresentationVolatileDense2JsonStream
    Common base class for non Mallet volatile representations.
    InstanceRepresentationDenseVolatile
    Representation of a dense-representation, non-lasting learning instance.
